Comment: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehehehe! Hahaha! Ehehehe!
Comment: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehehehe!
Comment: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehehehe!
Comment: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehehehe.
Comment: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.31,orig,,0,0,0,,That flat-chest...
Comment: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:02.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest.
Comment: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? What about your chest?
Comment: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Yes, your chest?
Comment: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.10,orig,,0,0,0,,N-No, ma'am.
Comment: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just talking to myself.
Comment: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.70,orig,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Comment: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.10,orig,,0,0,0,,He doesn't quit.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.00,orig,,0,0,0,,The more damage he takes, the stronger he gets!
Comment: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:02.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Ranta, I'm counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.10,orig,,0,0,0,,Don't die, Haruhiro, you idiot!
Comment: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.60,orig,,0,0,0,,I have to keep fighting in a situation like this?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.05,orig,,0,0,0,,You're ruthless, Ranta.
Comment: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:32.60,orig,,0,0,0,,No, he's moving really slowly.
Comment: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.95,orig,,0,0,0,,What happened to Death Spots?
Comment: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.65,orig,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Moguzo.
Comment: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Like Cleaver #1 or something.
Comment: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Took long enough.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.50,orig,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Comment: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:59.15,orig,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't accept Manato's death at that time yet.
Comment: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:02.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Well, there was something I wanted to ask you.
Comment: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.20,orig,,0,0,0,,What is it?

Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What—I guess they're pretty friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I'm a Dark Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O Darkness, master of Vices,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daemon{Demon} Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wimpy Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wimpy wooly caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only calling me a caterpillar now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zodiaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I really need to get out of this mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no way, no way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,Die, just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already half dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,Just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Die and be in Skullhell-sama's embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be embraced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.75,Alt,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.76,Alt,,0,0,0,,Caterpillar, caterpillar, caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm a caterpillar after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over our priorities again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our top priority is for all five of us to get back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is rescuing Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll do as much as we can, but we can't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you probably know that I don't like Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts my feelings when he calls me "flat-chested,"\Nand he doesn't stop even when I tell him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to like someone like that, even if you asked me to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if I were all alone in this mine,\NI'd be really scared, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I think about how Ranta must be feeling right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he would die from something like this,\Nhe would have died many times by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.60,Alt,,0,0,0,,Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the time to think about Vices!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,He got up here after being surrounded like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing if he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,His strength to live is stronger than most, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,The rest of us don't have that kind of tenacity to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Stay alive, Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:02.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have fondled her flat chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just call out to someone so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost gave me a heart attack, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my last arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Yume!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you run, Ranta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to, scum{you idiot}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are all watery, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hurting all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to see you alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I wanted to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-When I thought I would never see all\Nyour pretty little faces again, my chest—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.40,fix,,0,0,0,,What about your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your chest feel tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cheeest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My chest—!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.65,fix,,0,0,0,,Y-o-u-r cheeeest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you flat-chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, and I'll say it million times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flatchest,flatchest,flatchest—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to stop healing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.10,fix,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Ortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long day, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down until we get back to Ortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about what Ranta meant\Nwhen he said, "Aren't you our leader?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:59.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Because to me, Manato was our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:06.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,And to be honest, there was something inside me\Nthat thought I had to become like Manato, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:21.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Manato said that everyone has strengths and weaknesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,...but I don't know what Manato was bad at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:31.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,As for me, I have a lot of things that I'm\Nnot good at and that I need to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:37.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,My comrades make up for those\Nweaknesses by helping me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,and maybe that's how we've found a balance in our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:48.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't know if I'm actually being a proper leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:55.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,But if things are running smoothly,\Nthat's probably the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:02.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Like for Ranta and me, if we can work\Nwell during a fight, it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's because that's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to use magic for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At the most, I can cast one Cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go meditate somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:25.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand magic, but Shihoru looks drained, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try not to bother the Lesser Kobolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.06,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(671,217)\frz38}Grimgar of Fantasy\Nand Ash
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.70,fix,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.10,fix,,0,0,0,,You're dogged!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Death Spots gets stronger from the wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He gets stronger than this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing we can do, but can we outrun him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,It'll be impossible on this straight path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Someone... at least one of us needs to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, my body started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrust you!{for consistence sake}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:35.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,...are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:47.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yes... get out of here... everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.10,fix,,0,0,0,,Don't die, stupid Haruhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.60,fix,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't give up in a situation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're demon, shitty Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,...you're so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,...so I can't give up just yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:41.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry... come back and cast Dispel on me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe we can meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,...a battle of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's a battle of life and death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,So I'm not going to give up, and I'll keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll keep living until I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:19.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,He stopped—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.05,fix_it,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.00,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.60,fix_it,,0,0,0,,He's moving really slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Haru{Hal}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro-kun, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.95,fix,,0,0,0,,What about Death Spots?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This jog your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A bounty of thirty golds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta suggested to discuss how we\Nshould split it after you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was because you're the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and when we went back to get you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... when you went back to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were lying next the Date Spots, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Date"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you mean "Death Spots."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so... wait is that—?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my sword was broken anyway, and\Nit seemed wieldy so I thought I'd try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wieldy"? You're amazing, Moguzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use it like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of taking it to a swordsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we've decided on one of the\Nways we'll be using the bounty on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's done, we need to give it a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Cleaver-kun One or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess it's kinda cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I fixed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:35.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,The slight weight and feeling of it settled onto me...\Nand somewhere inside me, I felt calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was a mysterious feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,And suddenly, it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Only now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, I heard all about it, Haruhirocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed Spots, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm super jelly jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not jelly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Austraaaliaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Australia!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad... really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For what I did when Manato died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:59.15,fix,,0,0,0,,I just... couldn't accept Manato's death yet... at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should say thanks, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinks are on us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:20:59.45,fix,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.30,fix,,0,0,0,,...there was something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was being a leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...tough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it been tough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...looks like you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:33.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm different from who I was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I will be like tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:43.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Day by day, we live in the today and keep living...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...to meet our future selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back, Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,As I continue living in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,...I have memories that grow dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:33.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,The memories from what I should call the world I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:36.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,The feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:39.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,...that I had forgotten something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:45.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...worried and irritated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,It did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:50.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,But now, things are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,The solid feeling of the stone beneath me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and the smell of the air I breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:01.99,Italics,,0,0,0,,...make me feel like I'm really right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,And that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:13.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,I now have things that I don't want to forget,\Nand things that I shouldn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,And I don't plan to ever forget those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:20.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,...as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:34.96,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\fnTimes New Roman\c&H000000&\bord0\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(173,118)\fade(1300,0)}See You Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:34.96,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\fnTimes New Roman\c&H000000&\bord0\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1139,503)\fade(1300,0)}Grimgar of\NFantasy and Ash
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:50.55,song,,0,0,0,,Having fun, laughing, getting hurt, and crying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:57.65,song,,0,0,0,,Living in the presence of one another
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:02.00,song,,0,0,0,,Those moments in daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:06.15,song,,0,0,0,,Become precious memories
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:16.45,song,,0,0,0,,The ever-changing twilight becomes a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:28.25,song,,0,0,0,,Once, I saw in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:37.05,song,,0,0,0,,The winds of the future blowing in my reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:46.00,song,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I can meet you again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:54.95,song,,0,0,0,,This long, long road I've walked
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:18:01.00,song,,0,0,0,,Will bring me to another new world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:21.60,song,,0,0,0,,I've been through meetings and farewells
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:30.45,song,,0,0,0,,Days pass by one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:36.35,song,,0,0,0,,With memories I won't forget anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:06.00,song,,0,0,0,,Drawing what's happening now on the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:15.10,song,,0,0,0,,The next morning will bring tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:23.95,song,,0,0,0,,Soon, moving forward and farther ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:32.80,song,,0,0,0,,Going towards the future as I am now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:41.50,song,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I can meet you again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:50.40,song,,0,0,0,,This long, long road I've walked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:56.40,song,,0,0,0,,Will bring me to another new world
